# Lesson 07 Livebook: Duplicates Across Time

Identity has to survive the wormhole.

```elixir
Mix.install([
  {:wormhole_protocol, path: "../07_duplicates_across_time"}
])
```

## Run The Duplicate Scenario

```elixir
story = WormholeProtocol.duplicates_across_time_story!()

%{
  duplicate: story.duplicate,
  seen_command_ids: story.seen_command_ids
}
```

## Inspect The Accepted Allocation History

```elixir
story.allocations
```
